      <section id="intro" class="intro-section">
	<h2>Welcome to A Guide to Digital Drawing Platforms</h2>
	<div class="intro-content">
	  <p>Welcome to A Guide to Digital Drawing Platforms, your ultimate resource for exploring the best tools for digital illustration! Whether you're a beginner looking for the right software or an experienced artist wanting to try something new, we've got you covered.</p>

	  <div class="section-highlight">
	    <h3>🖌️ Top Digital Drawing Platforms Used by Artists in Asia</h3>
	    <p>Discover the most popular platforms that professional and aspiring artists use across Asia. Each software has its strengths—some excel in manga and comics, while others provide the closest experience to traditional painting.</p>
	  </div>
	</div>
      </section>        <section id="clip-studio" class="platform">
	<div class="platform-header">
	  <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/66/Clip_Studio_Paint_app_logo.png" alt="Logo de Clip Studio Paint" class="software-logo">
	  <h2>✨ Clip Studio Paint – The Ultimate Tool for Manga & Illustration</h2>
	</div>
	<div class="platform-content">
	  <div class="text-content">
	    <div class="platform-description">
	      <p>Clip Studio Paint is widely recognized as one of the most powerful tools for digital illustrators, particularly among comic and manga artists. Originally developed in Japan, it has gained global popularity due to its extensive set of specialized features.</p>
	    </div>
	    <div class="platform-intro">
	      <h3>🚀 Perfect for: Comic creators, manga artists, and illustrators who want full creative control</h3>
	    </div>
	    <div class="features">
	      <h4>🔹 Why Choose Clip Studio Paint?</h4>
	      <ul>
		<li>✅ Industry-standard for manga and comic creation with professional-grade tools used by studios worldwide</li>
		<li>✅ Advanced inking tools with customizable pen stabilization for creating smooth, precise linework</li>
		<li>✅ Comprehensive 3D models and pose libraries for accurate figure drawing and composition</li>
		<li>✅ Extensive brush customization system with thousands of downloadable options</li>
		<li>✅ Flexible pricing with one-time purchase for desktop and affordable monthly plans for mobile</li>
	      </ul>
	    </div>
	    <div class="fun-fact">
	      <h4>🔍 Did you know?</h4>
	      <p>Many professional manga artists in Japan use Clip Studio Paint, including those working for Shonen Jump!</p>
	    </div>
	  </div>
	  <img src="https://celcliptipsprod.s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/official/introduction_img_pc01_en.png" alt="Interfaz de Clip Studio Paint" class="software-screenshot">
	</div>
      </section>        <section id="medibang" class="platform">
	<div class="platform-header">
	  <img src="https://cdn6.aptoide.com/imgs/3/2/e/32e65dca82d6c3b5ce0029d9ce401a12_icon.png" alt="Logo de MediBang Paint" class="software-logo">
	  <h2>🎭 MediBang Paint – The Best Free Software for Comic Artists</h2>
	</div>
	<div class="platform-content">
	  <div class="text-content">
	    <div class="platform-description">
	      <p>MediBang Paint is a free, lightweight digital painting software that provides a solid set of features tailored for comic artists and illustrators. Its user-friendly interface and cloud-based functionality make it an excellent option for beginners and artists on the go.</p>
	    </div>
	    <div class="platform-intro">
	      <h3>🚀 Perfect for: Beginners and budget-conscious artists</h3>
	    </div>
	    <div class="features">
	      <h4>🔹 Why Choose MediBang Paint?</h4>
	      <ul>
		<li>✅ Completely FREE with unlimited cloud storage for your artwork and materials</li>
		<li>✅ Intuitive interface designed specifically for digital art beginners</li>
		<li>✅ Professional-grade comic panel tools with customizable layouts and templates</li>
		<li>✅ Seamless online collaboration features for team projects and feedback</li>
		<li>✅ Cross-platform compatibility across all major devices and operating systems</li>
	      </ul>
	    </div>
	    <div class="pro-tip">
	      <h4>💡 Pro Tip</h4>
	      <p>Perfect for beginners who want to explore digital art without any initial investment!</p>
	    </div>
	  </div>
	  <img src="https://medibangpaint.com/wp-content/themes/medibang/img-v2/paint_download_img2.png" alt="Interfaz de MediBang Paint" class="software-screenshot">
	</div>
      </section>        <section id="sai" class="platform">
	<div class="platform-header">
	  <img src="https://images-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com/f/b4393375-c298-43cb-a734-de19fa2f2f77/d3epm9f-fbbc62d6-998e-480b-a4bd-959d48fdcc3c.png?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..IdQJE3bueVx6GjMMTcMmHoCP4W4BJe_540A5_zZyZoo" alt="Logo de Paint Tool SAI" class="software-logo">
	  <h2>🎨 PaintTool SAI – The Smoothest Line Art Experience</h2>
	</div>
	<div class="platform-content">
	  <div class="text-content">
	    <div class="platform-description">
	      <p>PaintTool SAI is known for its lightweight yet powerful digital painting engine. It's particularly popular in Japan and among artists who focus on anime-style illustrations due to its precise brush engine and minimalistic interface.</p>
	    </div>
	    <div class="platform-intro">
	      <h3>🚀 Perfect for: Precise digital painting and clean linework</h3>
	    </div>
	    <div class="features">
	      <h4>🔹 Why Choose PaintTool SAI?</h4>
	      <ul>
		<li>✅ Industry-leading smooth brush engine for exceptional line quality and control</li>
		<li>✅ Clean, minimalist interface focused on maximizing your workspace efficiency</li>
		<li>✅ Advanced pen stabilization system for creating perfectly smooth lines</li>
		<li>✅ Optimized for detailed work with powerful layer blending capabilities</li>
		<li>✅ Lightweight performance ensuring smooth operation on most computers</li>
	      </ul>
	    </div>
	    <div class="pro-tip">
	      <h4>💡 Pro Tip</h4>
	      <p>SAI is perfect for artists who value precision and simplicity!</p>
	    </div>
	  </div>
	  <img src="https://www.systemax.jp/image/sai_shot.jpg" alt="Interfaz de Paint Tool SAI" class="software-screenshot">
	</div>
      </section>        <section id="procreate" class="platform">
	<div class="platform-header">
	  <img src="https://assets.procreate.art/img/procreate-icon-search-display.png" alt="Logo de Procreate" class="software-logo">
	  <h2>🏆 Procreate – The iPad Artist's Choice</h2>
	</div>
	<div class="platform-content">
	  <div class="text-content">
	    <div class="platform-description">
	      <p>Procreate is one of the most advanced digital art applications designed exclusively for iPad users. It has gained immense popularity for its intuitive touch-based controls, robust performance, and high-quality brush engine, making it a favorite among digital painters and illustrators.</p>
	    </div>
	    <div class="platform-intro">
	      <h3>🚀 Perfect for: Digital artists on the go</h3>
	    </div>
	    <div class="features">
	      <h4>🔹 Why Choose Procreate?</h4>
	      <ul>
		<li>✅ Seamlessly optimized for iPad with intuitive Apple Pencil integration</li>
		<li>✅ Professional-grade brush engine with customizable brush studio</li>
		<li>✅ Built-in time-lapse recording perfect for creating art tutorials</li>
		<li>✅ Powerful animation tools with easy-to-use frame-by-frame capabilities</li>
		<li>✅ Regular updates with new features and continuous performance improvements</li>
	      </ul>
	    </div>
	    <div class="fun-fact">
	      <h4>🔍 Did you know?</h4>
	      <p>Procreate is used by many professional artists in the gaming and film industry!</p>
	    </div>
	  </div>
	  <img src="https://cdn.macstories.net/2019-12-06-15-47-25-1637677969065.jpeg" alt="Interfaz de Procreate" class="software-screenshot">
	</div>
      </section>        <section id="corel" class="platform">
	<div class="platform-header">
	  <img src="https://store-images.s-microsoft.com/image/apps.13681.14479587561533360.6a8a5209-fe85-439e-9df6-8ad93fdd7f6b.08daed1c-bbcc-4017-844c-9f08c411aa18" alt="Logo de Corel Painter" class="software-logo">
	  <h2>🖌️ Corel Painter – Traditional Media Goes Digital</h2>
	</div>
	<div class="platform-content">
	  <div class="text-content">
	    <div class="platform-description">
	      <p>Corel Painter is one of the most sophisticated digital painting programs available, particularly known for its ability to mimic traditional painting techniques. It's a favorite among fine artists, illustrators, and those who want to recreate real-world painting techniques in a digital space.</p>
	    </div>
	    <div class="platform-intro">
	      <h3>🚀 Perfect for: Traditional artists transitioning to digital</h3>
	    </div>
	    <div class="features">
	      <h4>🔹 Why Choose Corel Painter?</h4>
	      <ul>
		<li>✅ Unmatched realistic traditional media simulation across multiple styles</li>
		<li>✅ Professional-grade color blending system mimicking real paint behavior</li>
		<li>✅ Extensive collection of customizable artistic tools and brushes</li>
		<li>✅ Advanced canvas textures simulating various traditional media surfaces</li>
		<li>✅ Comprehensive workflow optimization tools for professional artists</li>
	      </ul>
	    </div>
	    <div class="pro-tip">
	      <h4>💡 Pro Tip</h4>
	      <p>Best choice for artists who want to maintain their traditional art style in digital format!</p>
	    </div>
	  </div>
	  <img src="https://image.2gosoftware.eu/img/1250/750/catalog/Corel/2022/Corel_Painter_2022_PC/MAC/Color-Selection.PNG" alt="Interfaz de Corel Painter" class="software-screenshot">
	</div>
