    <footer>
      <div class="final-thoughts">
	<h3>💡 Final Thoughts: Which One is Right for You?</h3>
	<ul>
	  <li>✨ If you love manga & comics: Try Clip Studio Paint or MediBang Paint</li>
	  <li>✨ If you prefer anime-style illustrations: PaintTool SAI is a great choice</li>
	  <li>✨ If you want a mobile-friendly app: Procreate is the way to go</li>
	  <li>✨ If you want a traditional painting feel: Corel Painter is your best bet</li>
	</ul>
